  "texts": [
    "In addition, the alignment is also subject to the greatest uncertainty.",
    "Consequently, the mode tracking algorithm used to obtain the natural frequencies can, at times, misclassify the data and introduce large data scatter.",
    "This effect is especially prominent during damage (Jonscher et al., 2023; Wickramarachchi et al., 2023).",
    "As a result, a number of bending modes that are affected by these misclassifications are excluded from analysis in order to avoid progression of these errors further down the line.",
    "The torsional modes are also excluded from the input features in this work."
  ],
